  <description>
    <p>Electronic Quran Browser.</p>
    <ul>
      <li>Support Audio Tilawa (mp3 from ayat) And add Option To add Audio tilawa from ayat files (*.ayt)</li>
      <li>Support Auto Scroll + Run Tilawa</li>
      <li>Support Tarajem (from ayat) And add Option To add Tajarem from ayat files (*.ayt)</li>
      <li>Support Tafasir (from ayat) And add Option To add Tafasir from ayat files (*.ayt)</li>
      <li>Support Speed Up/Down Auto scroll </li>
      <li>Support save/load last current sura aya</li>
      <li>Support search for sura</li>
    </ul>
  </description>

